<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV50">
<l>veṇṭiraikka ruṅkaṭalci vantuvēva muṉṉornāḷ</l>
<l>tiṇṭiṟaṟci laikkaivāḷi viṭṭavīrar cērumū</l>
<l>reṇṭicaikka ṇaṅkaḷumi ṟaiñciyāṭu tīrttanīr</l>
<l>vaṇṭiraitta cōlaivēli maṉṉucīra raṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The town of the Warrior who, in the past, dispatched an arrow</l>
<l>with a robustly vigorous bow in hand in such a way that</l>
<l>the white-waved black ocean turned red and boiled away,</l>
<l>is Raṅgam of enduring fame, which has groves with humming bees as [its] fences</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] in whose pure water even the crowds from the eight quarters</l>
<l rend="indent">bathe worshipfully.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
